Our Organization



Highmark Health's businesses include the Highmark Health Plan, one of America's largest Blue Cross Blue Shield insurers; a growing regional hospital and physician network; and leading companies that offer dental solutions, reinsurance solutions, population health management, and innovative, technology solutions.


We serve individual consumers and fellow businesses in all 50 states and the District of Columbia. We're headquartered in Pittsburgh , as are several of our businesses.


And our legacy is strong and deep,beginning in the year 1848. Learn more about our companies.

Mission

To offer qualitative and comprehensive services in a patient-friendly environment with a focus on clinical excellence, safety, dignity and transparency, while staying affordable and accessible to every patient in need.

Vison

To create a world-class medical facility, wherein patients are treated with compassion.
